      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything just feels so empty lately. like, no matter what i do, it doesn't actually matter. the universe is just this massive, cold expanse of nothing and we're just tiny accidents that are gonna be forgotten anyway. there's no point in trying to find meaning where there isn't any.",
